---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Verkada Connectivity | Blue Cap IT — Gold Partner" description="Verkada cellular gateways, managed switches, and network connectivity solutions. LTE/5G failover and zero-touch deployment. Blue Cap IT — Verkada Gold Partner. Call (410) 858-4031.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="verkada.html">Verkada Solutions</a> <span>/</span> Connectivity</div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:center;">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Verkada Solution</div>
          <h1>Networking &amp; <span class="grad">Connectivity</span></h1>
          <p class="section-sub">Cellular gateways and managed switches that keep your Verkada devices online — even when wired internet goes down. Cloud-managed, zero-touch deployment.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Connectivity Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost btn-sm">📞 (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img src="/connectivity-hero.png" alt="Verkada Connectivity — Cellular Gateways and Managed Switches" style="width:100%;border-radius:1rem;" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="feature-list">
        <div class="feature-row">
          <div class="feature-visual"><div class="feature-visual-bg"></div><div class="big-icon">📡</div></div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Cellular Gateways for Always-On Connectivity</h3>
            <p>Verkada's GC31 indoor and GC31-E outdoor cellular gateways provide LTE/5G backup — or primary WAN connectivity — for your Verkada devices. When wired internet is unavailable or unreliable, cellular gateways keep cameras, access control, and sensors online.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>LTE/5G failover when wired internet drops</li>
              <li>Primary WAN option for sites without wired service</li>
              <li>GC31 for indoor installations, GC31-E for outdoor</li>
              <li>Automatic failover — no manual intervention needed</li>
              <li>Ideal for remote sites, construction zones, and pop-ups</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-row rev">
          <div class="feature-visual"><div class="feature-visual-bg"></div><div class="big-icon">🔌</div></div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Managed Switches &amp; Network Infrastructure</h3>
            <p>Verkada's cloud-managed network switches simplify deployment and monitoring of your physical security network. PoE-enabled switches power cameras, access controllers, and sensors — all visible and manageable from Verkada Command.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>PoE and PoE+ for powering Verkada devices</li>
              <li>Cloud-managed through Verkada Command</li>
              <li>Real-time port status and traffic monitoring</li>
              <li>Automatic firmware updates</li>
              <li>Stackable options for scalable deployments</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-row">
          <div class="feature-visual"><div class="feature-visual-bg"></div><div class="big-icon">☁️</div></div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Zero-Touch Deployment via Verkada Command</h3>
            <p>Every Verkada connectivity device is managed through the same Verkada Command platform you already use for cameras, access control, and sensors. Plug in a gateway or switch and it auto-provisions — no command-line configuration, no truck rolls.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>Automatic device provisioning on power-up</li>
              <li>Unified management alongside all Verkada devices</li>
              <li>Remote troubleshooting and diagnostics</li>
              <li>Centralized firmware and security updates</li>
              <li>Role-based access for network administrators</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="specs-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Hardware</div>
      <h2>Connectivity <span class="grad">Hardware</span></h2>
      <div class="specs-grid">
        <div class="spec-card"><h4>📡 Indoor Cellular Gateway (GC31)</h4><ul><li>LTE/5G cellular failover</li><li>Compact indoor form factor</li><li>Auto-failover when wired WAN drops</li><li>Cloud-managed via Verkada Command</li><li>Supports multiple Verkada devices</li></ul></div>
        <div class="spec-card"><h4>🏗️ Outdoor Cellular Gateway (GC31-E)</h4><ul><li>Weatherproof outdoor enclosure</li><li>LTE/5G primary or backup WAN</li><li>Built for construction sites &amp; remote locations</li><li>PoE powered — single cable install</li><li>Extended temperature range</li></ul></div>
        <div class="spec-card"><h4>🔌 Network Switches</h4><ul><li>Cloud-managed PoE/PoE+ switches</li><li>8, 24, and 48-port options</li><li>Real-time port monitoring</li><li>Automatic firmware updates</li><li>Stackable for large deployments</li></ul></div>
        <div class="spec-card"><h4>⚡ Zero-Touch Deployment</h4><ul><li>Plug in and auto-provision</li><li>No CLI or manual configuration</li><li>Managed in Verkada Command</li><li>Remote diagnostics &amp; troubleshooting</li><li>Automatic security patches</li></ul></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="cta-band">
    <div class="section-label">Stay Connected Everywhere</div>
    <h2>Reliable Connectivity<br/><span class="grad">Installed by Blue Cap IT</span></h2>
    <p>Blue Cap IT will assess your connectivity needs, recommend the right Verkada gateways and switches, and handle installation end-to-end.</p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Request a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">📞 (410) 858-4031</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@bluecapit.com" class="btn-ghost">✉️ info@bluecapit.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
